  "detailed_description": "<strong>关于这款游戏</strong><br><br>在充满怪物的洞天中，坚持到最后并击杀boss，夺取洞天的灵气！通过类似幸运房东的升级系统组成你的牌库，对你的能力进行提升、使能力进化！你将成为洞天的幸存者，还是会成为一抔黄土？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/df21b839740ad10ffd4161670172d999.poster.avif?t=1708620811\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/df21b839740ad10ffd4161670172d999.webm?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/df21b839740ad10ffd4161670172d999.mp4?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>升炼系统：升级系统借鉴幸运房东，通过构建不同体系的物品，通过升练为技能升级<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/6c45fe30544d2abef2f36bf09e815f2e.poster.avif?t=1708620811\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/6c45fe30544d2abef2f36bf09e815f2e.webm?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/6c45fe30544d2abef2f36bf09e815f2e.mp4?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>能力系统: 多种能力，根据你的喜好搭配不同技能，通过升炼系统使技能升级，将使技能获得强化或进化，也许能获得更多被动能力，解锁不一样的惊喜体验<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/64908db0ef8e41694634e7af04472ef0.poster.avif?t=1708620811\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/64908db0ef8e41694634e7af04472ef0.webm?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2786280/extras/64908db0ef8e41694634e7af04472ef0.mp4?t=1708620811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>多样化的角色：通过选择角色根据其特性来提升战力，解锁角色来解锁新的能力<br><br></li><li>时间随意: 10-20分钟一局，可以随时放松</li></ul>",
